snippet.title: HITMAN arrives on STADIA
snippet.description: The HITMAN World of Assassination trilogy is coming to Stadia! HITMAN 1 will be available free in Stadia Pro and arrives alongside HITMAN 2 on September 1. The trilogy reaches its dramatic conclusion in January 2021 with HITMAN 3. More details: https://www.ioi.dk/stadia-announcement/
